<p>No record of lambs kept.—</p>
<p>Pray excuse my delay in answering your letter.—</p>
<p>I am yours truly | John Graham <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/> <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/></p>
<p rend="left">George Cupples Esq | Guard Bridge</p> 
